    "body": "You should be able to combine two root CA certificates into one file. Could you show us the combined root pem file?\r\n\r\nYou can take the following as an example \r\nhttps://github.com/grpc/grpc/blob/master/etc/roots.pem\r\n\r\nEach certificate is separated with\r\n-----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----\r\n....\r\n-----END CERTIFICATE-----"
